																		Something I had to write.
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164135" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;" >WrongJohnSilver</a></span> <span class="odate time_1510118493 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">08 Nov 2017 05:21</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3628163">
									

<p>Sometimes, something sticks in your head and heart, and you need to get it out.</p>
<p>Memetic kill agent is by <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/torley/8553542912" target="_blank">Torley</a>, with added JPEG.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510145223" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;">Shaggydredlocks</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adam-smascher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(587467); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=587467&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510145223" alt="Adam Smascher" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=587467)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adam-smascher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(587467); return false;">Adam Smascher</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=304355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510145223" alt="Silberescher" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=304355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;">Silberescher</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510145223" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http: